title: MediChain: Decentralized Medical Record Keeping System
description: MediChain is a end-to-end decentralized medical record keeping system based on EVMcompatible public blockchain using decentralized peer-to-peer solution - IPFS for storing the sensitive medical data on blockchain secured by 2048 bit RSA asymmetric key encryption. This system also uses The Graph as an indexer for fast and complex queries of blockchain data making the system even more scalable. This system categorizes the medical files of the patient in four categories: vaccination, chronic, acute and, accidental which makes the retrieval of medical information very efficient without any manual work at patient‚Äôs end.
